name: Agog 13 Semi Spiral Golden
description: @__lindaloh__ 3D sculpture gold toned semi spiral form. One of a collection of 20 individual sculptural pieces from my VR world "Agog", 2021. They are variously luminous, poetic, evocative, shiny, scribbly, wacky, simple, sleek, golden, wonky, clashing, compelling, weird, colourful, minimal, maximal, simple, ethereal...
